 MANIFEST.in      |  2 ++
 requirements.txt |  3 +++
 setup.py         | 28 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 33 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 MANIFEST.in
 create mode 100644 requirements.txt
